    title: 'Disclosing Your HIV Status: A Personal and Empowering Journey',
    excerpt: 'A guide to the emotional and practical aspects of disclosing your HIV status to partners, family, and friends.',
    category: 'Living with HIV',
    author: 'Dr. David Miller, PhD',
