    id: 'hiv-disclosure-in-workplace',
    title: 'HIV Disclosure in the Workplace: Knowing Your Rights',
    excerpt: 'A guide to the legal and personal considerations of disclosing your HIV status to an employer.',
    category: 'Living with HIV',
